      "avatar_template": "/letter_avatar_proxy/v4/letter/e/b19c9b/{size}.png",
      "created_at": "2025-05-26T20:54:59.413Z",
      "cooked": "<p>Hi everybody,<br>\nI am fed up of using my spin bike with Favero power pedals, I want something more advanced and use ERG mode\u2026</p>\n<p>I don\u2019t have a dedicated room so space is a bit of a problem, the spin bike I currently use is just perfect in terms of measurements, my gaming/training platform is Zwift and the whole setup has to be moved from one room to another to let me train\u2026</p>\n<p>I don\u2019t want to spend more than 1600 Euro and I selected below indoor trainers up to now:</p>\n<p>Smart Zbike 2.0 1.600 Euro<br>\nZwift Ride with Kickr Core 1.300 Euro</p>\n<p>All opinions and suggestions welcomed, it is a big investment and I want to buy the right thing\u2026</p>\n<p>Ciao Erik Il Rosso</p>",
