      "created_at": "2025-05-29T06:12:28.733Z",
      "cooked": "<p>Hi Alex,<br>\nI think that my final choice is going to be Zbike\u2026</p>\n<p>Zwift Ride costs less and it\u2019s perfectly integrated in the Zwift environment that I use but I am not totally convinced\u2026</p>\n<p>One final thought, am I mistaken or are you suggesting to use the Favero pedals even on the new bike ??? If the answer is yes could you pls tell me why ???</p>\n<p>Ciao, Erik Il Rosso</p>",
